OL,3,CCleaner jailed after being caught
OL,4,Cstealing money from 92-year-old woman
OL,6,FA cleaner from Warrington has been
OL,7,Fjailed for nine months after admitting
OL,8,Fto stealing from a 92-year-old woman
OL,9,Fwhile cleaning at her home.
OL,11,FAlison Lavell, 59, was sentenced at
OL,12,FLiverpool Crown Court on Tuesday 10
OL,13,FSeptember after previously pleading
OL,14,Fguilty to two counts of theft.
