OL,3,CCleaner jailed after being caught
OL,4,Cstealing money from 92-year-old woman
OL,6,FThe court heard that on 12 January
OL,7,F2024, Cheshire Police received a
OL,8,Freport from the victim's son, who
OL,9,Fsuspected that Lavell had been
OL,10,Fstealing money from his 92-year-old
OL,11,Fmother that was supposed to be given
OL,12,Fto her carers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
