OL,3,CCleaner jailed after being caught
OL,4,Cstealing money from 92-year-old woman
OL,6,FThe caller reported that around #500
OL,7,Fhad gone missing by the time the
OL,8,Ffamily had been made aware and they
OL,9,Flater provided Cheshire Police with
OL,10,Fvideo footage from a hidden camera
OL,11,Ffrom inside the elderly woman's home
OL,12,Fthat showed Lavell, who was her
OL,13,Fpersonal cleaner at the time, taking
OL,14,Fwhat they believed was #20 from her
OL,15,Fpurse on 2 January 2024.
OL,17,FA second piece of video footage taken
OL,18,Fa week later showed Lavell again
OL,19,Freaching into the purse of the victim
OL,20,Fand taking a further #20.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
