OL,3,CCleaner jailed after being caught
OL,4,Cstealing money from 92-year-old woman
OL,6,FLavell was subsequently arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of theft but denied any
OL,8,Fknowledge of the 92-year-old's money
OL,9,Fgoing missing.
OL,11,FDespite claiming she was innocent,
OL,12,Fclaiming she had picked up a
OL,13,Fprescription for the woman from her
OL,14,Fpurse and not cash, Lavell was charged
OL,15,Fwith two counts of theft and went to
OL,16,Ftrial. After initially pleading not
OL,17,Fguilty, she would later change her
OL,18,Fplea to guilty after CCTV footage was
OL,19,Fshown to her in court.
