OL,3,CCleaner jailed after being caught
OL,4,Cstealing money from 92-year-old woman
OL,6,FAlison Lavell, of Alexandra Street,
OL,7,FWarrington, then appeared at Liverpool
OL,8,FCrown Court on Tuesday 10 September
OL,9,Fwhere she was jailed for nine months
OL,10,Fon each count, with the sentences to
OL,11,Fbe served concurrently.
OL,13,FPolice Constable Stephen Wolstenholme,
OL,14,Fof the Warrington Area Investigation
OL,15,FTeam, said: "Alison Lavell abused her
OL,16,Fposition of trust and stole the money
OL,17,Fof a vulnerable person who considered
OL,18,Fher a friend; I hope that her
OL,19,Fsentencing today provides the victim
OL,20,Fwith a sense of closure from this
OL,21,Fdistressing incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
